Title: SDS Special : Giving Up Coffee, IQ vs EQ and Asking the Right Questions with Vitaly Dolgov
Description: In this special episode of the Super Data Science Podcast, I chat with my friend and one of the World’s leading business turnaround consultants Vitaly Dolgov. You will get to listen to one of our casual chats. You will know the reason why Vitaly started giving up coffee, learn insights about IQ vs EQ and get ideas on his effective business coaching techniques.If you enjoyed this episode, check out show notes, resources, and more at https://www.superdatascience.com/special
